description	"Kyle Katarn

Class: Jedi
Brief Overview:
A saberist/gunner hybrid with Force powers that rewards flanking, skirmishing, and juggling his various options.

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Lightsaber
-- Yellow/Red styles
-- Saber Defense (1)
-- Blaster Defense (1)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)
-- Saber Throw (3) [CS1]
- Bryar Pistol (3)
- Stun Baton
- Thermal Grenade (1)
- Detonation Pack (1)
- Trip Mine (1)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (1)
- Pull (1)
- Sense (2)
- Grip (2)
- Lightning (1)
- Protect (2)
- Absorb (1)

^8Attributes:
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Fall
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

Kyle Katarn was a famous Force-sensitive Human male Rebel operative from Sulon and later a Jedi of the New Jedi Order. He was a former Imperial officer who defected to the Rebellion. After learning of Morgan Katarn's death at the hands of Jerec, Kyle Katarn chose to continue his murdered father's mission of protecting the Valley of the Jedi's immense power from being abused. In the process of fighting through Jerec's minions, Kyle managed to teach himself about the Force and the ways of the Jedi."
